<div> 
</div> 
<div>As a program of the Provincial Health Services Authority (PHSA), the BCCDC shares PHSA’s purpose, vision, values and teachings.&#160;</div> 
<div> 
   <br/> 
</div> 
<div>The Coast Salish teachings were gifted to PHSA by Coast Salish Knowledge Keeper, Shane Pointe, Siem Te’ta-in.<br/></div> 
<div> 
   <br/> 
</div> 
